Victoria Rowland https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Victoria_Rowland 0 Victoria Rowland is an Australian actress, having started out working behind the cameras as a production assistant and wardrobe stylist she remains best known for playing Margaret "Spike" Marsh in the television drama Prisoner during its final months in 1986. She also had a role in the TV movie Economy Class.
